    <item>
      <title>梅奥称银行债券实力增强，为其股票提供支撑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/banks-bond-strength-bolsters-case-for-their-stocks-mayo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行分析师迈克·梅奥表示，美国银行发行的债券利差收窄表明信贷投资者认为该类债券的风险较小，股票投资者应该注意这种看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/banks-bond-strength-bolsters-case-for-their-stocks-mayo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 19:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱预计美联储作出关键决定前美元将上涨 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/barclays-sees-dollar-rallying-1-ahead-of-fed-s-crucial-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱外汇策略师斯凯拉·蒙哥马利·科宁表示，由于交易员高估了美联储降息的幅度，并低估了周二的零售销售报告，美元有望上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/barclays-sees-dollar-rallying-1-ahead-of-fed-s-crucial-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 19:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
