    <item>
      <title>韦丹塔氧化铝厂水毁后产量未受影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/aluminum-prices-jump-after-another-alumina-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韦丹塔有限公司 (Vedanta Ltd.) 表示，印度一家工厂的蓄水设施周日发生溢流，预计其氧化铝生产不会受到任何影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/aluminum-prices-jump-after-another-alumina-disruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
